title: and Jax Taylor and Brittany Cartwright
description:
What happens in Vegas stays in Vegas... unless you're Jax Taylor and Brittany Cartwright from Vanderpump Rules!  Then what happens in Vegas moves on to Los Angeles and ends in marriage! Jax and Brittany get real about the start of their relationship, dealing with fame and paparazzi, adoring fans, and camera crews invading their lives. They also help LaLa and Randall answer listener questions, and weigh in on the whole Tom Sandoval-Stassi Schroeder spat.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
